INSERT INTO `wp_dyfl_posts` VALUES("64","1","2012-11-05 16:26:59","2012-11-05 16:26:59","<h2>Meet our pros! They make our club<br />
 the sweet spot for developing your game.</h2>
<div class=\"copy3\">The FRC pro staff is second to none. Manager <a href=\"http://www.frontenactennis.com/?p=69\">Terry Ward</a> has been with the club since 1982. His leadership and drive make FRC the dominant indoor tennis club in the St. Louis area.

<p>Second-in-command <a title=\"Stefan Kruger\" href=\"http://www.frontenactennis.com/?p=155\">Stefan Kruger</a> has been with us since 1998. He adds the structure to bring you and your family a consistently first-rate experience.</p>
<p>Together they lead one of the most dynamic groups of young pros anywhere.</p>
<p>Offering everything from private lessons to group classes, these young pros deliver the finest instruction in the country.</p>
<h3>The Frontenac way.</h3>
<p>At FRC we follow the traditional path: simple preparation, simple follow-through.</p>
<p>No swinging volleys. No <strong>modern</strong> forehands.</p>
<p>Tried-and-true has served us well since 1975.</p>
<p>We continue to emphasize the fundamentals that make a great tennis game.</p>
<p>Plus, you\'ll always get a warm smile and a welcome hand.</p>
<p>It\'s the Frontenac way.</p>
</div>","Our Pros","","publish","open","open","","pros","","","2016-10-29 19:45:03","2016-10-29 19:45:03","","0","http://frc-tennis.com/?page_id=64","0","page","","0");
INSERT INTO `wp_dyfl_posts` VALUES("111","1","2012-11-06 16:18:43","2012-11-07 00:18:43","<div class=\"one-third first\"><a href=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Karim2014-e1411765917974.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1509 size-medium\" title=\"Karim Madatali\" src=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Karim2014-e1411765917974-275x343.jpg\" alt=\"Photo: Karim Madatali\" width=\"275\" height=\"343\" /></a></div>
<div class=\"two-thirds\">The director of our <a href=\"../topguns.html\">Top Guns</a> program, Karim is a P1 USPTA Certified teaching pro who\'s been at Frontenac since 2002. He runs Monday Night Singles and men\'s interclub. In the summers, he\'s been the Director of Tennis at the Westborough Country Club since 2005.Originally from Vancouver, Canada, Karim earned several national top-30 singles rankings as a junior - and a Junior World Ranking in doubles.At Maryville University, he played #1 Singles and Doubles and earned First Team All-Conference honors from the St. Louis Intercollegiate Athletic Conference in 1999.

In 2006, the St. Louis District Tennis Association named Karim Adult Player of the Year after he finished 2005 as the #1 Singles Player in the St. Louis Area. That year, Karim and former FRC pro Kevin Lackey were the Association\'s #1 Doubles Team.He has also coached college tennis since 2000. As Maryville\'s head men\'s coach from 2000-2008, his players earned both All-District and Academic All-American Honors. Now he\'s the head coach at Fontbonne.Karim and his wife, Erica, have two girls.

