<div class=\"two-thirds\">
One of the top women players our area has produced and a member of the St. Louis Tennis Hall of Fame, Maria has been at Frontenac since 1980.
As a junior, she ranked as high as seventh in the world, reaching the finals of both the Junior French Open and the Junior U.S. Open. She also played at Wimbledon.
At Brigham Young University in Utah, Maria was All-American in 1978 and 1979.
