INSERT INTO `wp_dyfl_posts` VALUES("235","1","2012-11-07 23:24:01","2012-11-07 23:24:01","<iframe src=\"http://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/-Ht3_wPEjXc?rel=0\" width=\"853\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>

<h2>Ever wonder what goes on at a Ladies\' Interclub practice?</h2>

<div class=\"copy\">

Several regulars at our ladies\' Interclub practices say they\'re the highlight of their week.These fast-paced tennis clinics follow a specific format:
<ul>
    <li>a 20-minute warmup, often with cardio intent;</li>
    <li>Two drills that cover a specific theme, generally developed over several weeks;</li>
    <li>A game of doubles points that integrate specific skills from the theme (named <span class=\"emph\">craps</span>, after the casino game);</li>
    <li>A cooldown of real doubles or a combination of doubles and the game known variously as Queen of the Court, Three and Take Over or Rush \'n Crush.</li>
</ul>
<h4>The Frontenac difference.</h4>
At other clinics you may have taken, there\'s a pro or two circulating among four or five tennis courts – giving advice as the players set up the drills for themselves.

At Frontenac, there\'s a pro on every court, feeding in balls and making sure the drills teach the concepts as planned. They\'re also there to answer questions as they come up, about strokes, strategy and more. So in a 90-minute practice, more time gets spent on the theme of the day and less on chasing errant balls.
<h4>Take a look!</h4>
Here are several weeks\' worth of demos and drills boiled down to just under eight minutes of video from our 1 pm practice on Tuesdays.

Thanks to pros <a title=\"Mark McPhillips\" href=\"http://www.frontenactennis.com/mark-mcphillips/\">Mark McPhillips,</a> <a title=\"Carolyn Kramer\" href=\"http://www.frontenactennis.com/carolyn-kramer/\">Carolyn Kramer</a> and <a title=\"Clark Taylor\" href=\"http://www.frontenactennis.com/clark-taylor/\">Clark Taylor;</a> players Nancy Hinkson, Lisa Hilton and the rest of the Tuesday gang.

</div>","Ladies&#039; clinics and practices","","publish","open","open","","ever-wonder-what-goes-on-at-a-ladies-interclub-practice","","","2012-11-07 23:24:01","2012-11-07 23:24:01","","0","http://frc-tennis.com/?p=235","0","post","","2");
INSERT INTO `wp_dyfl_posts` VALUES("254","1","2012-11-08 09:43:32","2012-11-08 15:43:32","<div class=\"one-half\"><a href=\"http://frc-tennis.com/8-week-kickstart/kickstart-woman/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-255\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-255\" title=\"kickstart-woman\" src=\"http://www.frontenactennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/kickstart-woman.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"778\" /></a></div>

<div class=\"one-third\">
<h2>Got 8 weeks? Then come get your game on.</h2>
<h3>Frontenac’s Kickstart program gets you really playing – and having fun! In just 8 weeks.</h3>
<h4>You’ll learn:</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Forehands and backhands.</li>
    <li>Where to stand - and how to serve.</li>
    <li>Scoring and moving on the court.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Coming back to tennis?</h4>
Haven’t played in years? Kickstart’s a great way to restart your game. Join us for fun, fitness and great new friends!
<h4>Kickstart’s a steal.</h4>
<h2>Just 8 weeks for $100!</h2>
<h4>Bring a friend and get $10 off!</h4>
<h2>Plus: forget childcare worries.</h2>
<h4>Get your little ones in the game with our FRC-Tots! classes.</h4>
We\'ve got classes for preschoolers three days a week, and a Pee Wee class for five- and six-year-olds.
<h3>In just weeks, you could have a whole family of avid, happy tennis players!</h3>
<h4>Get started now!</h4>
Kickstart groups consist of 4-5 women and a pro. Kickstart classes are forming all the time!
<h4>To get started, call Jennifer Wilhelm-Zeuschel at 314-991-5599 or send her a quick note at <a href=\"mailto:jen@frontenactennis.com\">jen@frontenactennis.com</a>.</h4>
</div>","8-week Kickstart!","","publish","open","open","","kickstart","","","2012-11-08 09:43:32","2012-11-08 15:43:32","","0","http://frc-tennis.com/?p=254","0","post","","1");
INSERT INTO `wp_dyfl_posts` VALUES("289","1","2012-11-08 10:45:47","2012-11-08 16:45:47","<div class=\"one-half\">
<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-741\" src=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/David-Nayak03-275x269.jpg\" alt=\"David-Nayak03\" width=\"275\" height=\"269\" /></p>
<h1>The sweet spot for St. Louis tennis since 1974.</h1>
<p>Maybe we\'ve just been having too much fun on the courts to notice, but it\'s hard to believe we\'ve been around that long.</p>
<p>It makes sense, though.</p>
<h2>Because at Frontenac, it really is all about the tennis.</h2>
<p>So, of course, you\'ll find everything you\'d expect at a first-rate tennis club:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Ten very nicely lit indoor courts.</li>
	<li>Complete locker-room facilities with private showers. We renovated the ladies\' locker room in 2009.</li>
	<li>A snack bar with a full liquor license and a comfortable lounge.</li>
	<li>Plus, <a title=\"Meet Pam Busch –\" href=\"http://frc-tennis.com/meet-pam-busch/\">daytime child care - courtesy of every little kid\'s best friend, Pam Busch.</a></li>
</ul>
<p>But more important, you\'ll find great people to play with, <a title=\"Pros\" href=\"http://frc-tennis.com/pros/\">some of the best pros in the busines</a>s and a wealth of programs and activities to help you develop the best game you\'ve ever had.</p>
<p>And it all happens in a relaxed, casual atmosphere that\'s as much about family fun as it is about winning matches.</p>
<p>So if you\'re looking for a place to play, download our application and join Frontenac Racquet Club now.</p>
<p>Already a member? <a title=\"Program brochures!\" href=\"http://frc-tennis.com/program-brochures/\">Download our brochures and pick a tennis clinic, or play in a game.</a></p>
</div>","About FRC","","publish","open","open","","frontenac-racquet-club","","","2016-10-30 20:08:16","2016-10-30 20:08:16","","0","http://frc-tennis.com/?p=289","0","post","","0");
