Turn left onto German Boulevard and follow that road back around to the left, past Frontenac Bank and several other small buildings, one of which is Grassi\'s Italian restaurant. Now veer up to the right before turning left into the club parking lot.

From the north, go south on Lindbergh to the same light at Conway Road, and turn right onto German Boulevard. Then do that same loop-de-loop towards the back of the area, and you\'ll find us right there!

