INSERT INTO `wp_dyfl_posts` VALUES("958","1","2013-05-29 10:27:15","2013-05-29 16:27:15","Two more Hall of Fame inductees: Jane Pratt and Jack Eggmann.
<h3>Jane Pratt.</h3>
Rick Randall told the crowd about how Jane ran all the tournaments at Dwight Davis with a loving but firm hand - and a sharp eye on the books. And that was while maintaining a championship-level doubles game of her own, with her longtime partner, who was there to accept the award on Jane\'s behalf..

[caption id=\"attachment_961\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"298\"]<a href=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jane-Pratt-induction-Rick-Randall.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-961\" alt=\"Photo- Hall of Fame induction (3)\" src=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jane-Pratt-induction-Rick-Randall-298x249.jpg\" width=\"298\" height=\"249\" /></a> Rick Randall inducts Jane Pratt into the Hall of Fame.[/caption]

[caption id=\"attachment_962\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"298\"]<a href=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jane-Pratt-induction.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-962\" alt=\"Photo- Hall of Fame induction (2)\" src=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jane-Pratt-induction-298x311.jpg\" width=\"298\" height=\"311\" /></a> Jane Pratt\'s longtime doubles partner and close friend, accepting her induction into the Hall.[/caption]

[caption id=\"attachment_960\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"298\"]<a href=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jane-Pratt-induction-2.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-960\" alt=\"Photo- Hall of Fame induction (4)\" src=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jane-Pratt-induction-2-298x316.jpg\" width=\"298\" height=\"316\" /></a> Jane Pratt\'s longtime doubles partner and close friend, accepting her induction into the Hall.[/caption]
<h3>Jack Eggmann.</h3>
Tom O\'Neill spoke lovingly about Jack Eggmann\'s role as the archivist of the Hall of Fame. Then he introduced Jack\'s daughter, who shared her own memories of growing up around tennis and the history of the game, seen through her father\'s eyes.

[caption id=\"attachment_963\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"298\"]<a href=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Tom-ONeill-citation.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-963\" alt=\"Photo- Hall of Fame induction (1)\" src=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Tom-ONeill-citation-298x227.jpg\" width=\"298\" height=\"227\" /></a> Tom O\'Neill reads the citation inducting the late Jack Eggmann into the Hall of Fame to Jack\'s daughter.[/caption]

[caption id=\"attachment_959\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"298\"]<a href=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Eggmann-daughter.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-959\" alt=\"Photo- Hall of Fame induction (5)\" src=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Eggmann-daughter-298x288.jpg\" width=\"298\" height=\"288\" /></a> Jack Eggmann\'s daughter shares memories of life with the tennis archivist.[/caption]","Jane Pratt and Jack Eggmann enter the Hall of Fame.","","publish","open","open","","jane-pratt-and-jack-eggmann-enter-the-hall-of-fame","","","2013-05-29 10:27:15","2013-05-29 16:27:15","","0","http://www.frontenactennis.com/?p=958","0","post","","0");
