<!----PROGRAM------>

<div class=\"one-fourth\">
<h2>The Program</h2>
The Top Guns Competition program is for any player who would like to compete in local and regional tournaments, play high-school tennis and perhaps college tennis.<!--more-->
<h6>Players in the Top Guns program are required to:</h6>
<ul>
    <li>Play tennis at least three times a week. That includes any combination of classes, lessons, match plays and/or tournaments.</li>
    <li>Compete in local tournaments.</li>
    <li>Actively work toward improving their game in a serious and focused manner.</li>
</ul>
</div>

<!----LOGO------>

<div class=\"two-fifths\">
<h6><a href=\"http://www.frontenactennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/TG2016-competition.gif\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-183\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1944 size-thumb\" title=\"topguns-530\" src=\"http://www.frontenactennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/TG2016-competition.gif\" alt=\"Logo: Top Guns Competition\" width=\"300\" /></a></h6>
</div>

<!----PHILOSOPHY------>

<div class=\"one-fourth\">
<h2>The Philosophy</h2>
<h6>Small groups</h6>
8-10 students per class
<h6>Positive reinforcement</h6>
No yelling or screaming.
<h6>Good strokes, good grips</h6>
Basics are top priority.
<h6>Good fun</h6>
<ul>
    <li>Mon/Tues focus on singles.</li>
    <li>Wed/ Thurs focus on doubles.</li>
</ul>
<h6>Hard work</h6>
Players who don\'t focus on improving will be asked to leave the program.

