<p>Buy a Class Pass for $300, get TEN classes in a semester! Additional classes are just $30 each!</p>
<h6><a href=\"ICpractice.html\">Interclub practice. </a></h6>
<p>Run. Drill. Hit. Play. WIN MORE MATCHES.</p>
<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Red/Blue level, must play Interclub. </span><em>Tuesdays, 12 – 1:30 pm. $300 Class Pass gets you ten weeks in the semester. </em></p>
