<p>The perfect way to end the day: everything from stretches and strategies to cardio tennis. <em>Wednesdays, 8:30 – 10 pm or Thursdays, 6:30 – 8 pm. $40 a class, or buy a $300 Class Pass, good for ten.</em></p>
