<h6>Men\'s Drill and Doubles.</h6>
<p>Drill for an hour, play for a half. We cover strokes, strategy, offense, defense and everything in between. <em>Wednesdays, 8:30<em> – </em>10 pm, and Saturdays, 7:30<em> – </em>9 am.</em></p>
<p><a href=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Clinic5-volleys-6-e1469654115340.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-922 size-medium\" src=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Clinic5-volleys-6-e1469654115340-275x257.jpg\" alt=\"Photo: Jeff Fox in a clinic\" width=\"275\" height=\"257\" /></a></p>
