INSERT INTO `wp_dyfl_posts` VALUES("1675","1","2015-05-17 23:07:07","2015-05-18 06:07:07","Patrick and Chris Smith of Kansas City took home the pride of I-70 on May 2 at the seventh annual Frontenac Pro Doubles Classic.

Runners-up were KC\'s Scott Schibig and FRC\'s Mick Lyons, who filled in for an injured Jason Grubb.

