INSERT INTO `wp_dyfl_posts` VALUES("2010","1","2016-10-27 21:08:08","2016-10-27 21:08:08","<div class=\"one-third first\"><a href=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/WillBrown-e1411761848583.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1459 size-medium\" src=\"http://www.frctennis.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/WillBrown-e1411761848583-275x343.jpg\" alt=\"Pic: Will Brown\" width=\"275\" height=\"343\" /></a></div>

<div class=\"two-thirds\">A veteran USPTA Certified Professional who\'s worked extensively with juniors, Will Brown joined Frontenac in summer 2014.
We\'re used to thinking of summer as downtime around the club, but the FRC juniors\' tennis camp and annual improvements to the physical plant keep a lot of folks hopping.

<h4>A busy guy.</h4>
Since 2011 he\'s been a national coach with Junior Team Tennis.

In 2014, he coached a group of boys to a third-place finish in the USTA Spring Team National Championships.

In 2015, he coached a team of nationally ranked girls to the championship of that event.

At FRC, Will runs our invitation-only Top Guns Junior Elite program for tournament-level juniors under 12.
<h4>Contact info:</h4>
<a href=\"mailto:will@frc-tennis.com\">Email Will here</a> or text him at <a href=\"sms:+14172607143\">417.260.7143</a>. You can also call him at the club: <a href=\"tel:+13149915599\">314-991-5599</a>.
