<div class=\"two-thirds\">A Division Two college coach at several schools over the years, Peter is the head coach at Maryville University.
<h3>Playing days.</h3>
A St. Louis native, Peter played his college tennis at UMSL – also a D2 school – and still holds the all-time record for most singles wins in a career there.

